### Step1 注册域名勾选礼包套餐
![](https://main.qcloudimg.com/raw/185d45f8bcf6d9b7ede64a26c184b2a3.png)
### Step2 确认订单并支付
![](https://main.qcloudimg.com/raw/8c42b10e9614c71fe959a981883df14c.png)
### Step3 支付成功
![](https://main.qcloudimg.com/raw/e8c8909c86ccef6145d3e70e6324cac9.png)
### Step4 进入管理中心
![](https://main.qcloudimg.com/raw/885131f71f69075b9cb5ff6fdfda4572.png)
### Step5 如何找到网站订单？
进入域名管理后点击右上角“费用->我的订单”即可以扎到网站订单信息
![](https://main.qcloudimg.com/raw/c5a584727e90ddf7977fc25c320920c7.png)
### Step6 找到订单，点击详情
![](https://main.qcloudimg.com/raw/bca257fe246c70a5dab312694bef3a34.png)
### Step7 找到订单资源ID，并点击
![](https://main.qcloudimg.com/raw/683f51b9882cf71e16ab86dd8646e460.png)
### Step8 找到免登录地址，进入站点
![](https://main.qcloudimg.com/raw/a7d7cb5bd54b24bbcb517fb8d1f635fb.png)
### Step9 授权登陆中
![](https://main.qcloudimg.com/raw/11cf1957c98890e3b49b0227c9619008.png)
### Step10 成功登陆进入管理，去绑定域名准备上线吧！
![](https://main.qcloudimg.com/raw/2e766a2a1fda4eb22f165b3ba37c799b.png)
